HB 2172 Apr 22: drifting with large berg. This is the only berg sighted or reported this year south of 48.30N. This berg is slowly disintegrating & since being reported on the 14th in 47.02N 52.39W has moved slowly southward as far as 46.25N 52.11W on the 18th, thence northwestward to 46.35N 52.30W on the 19th. Apparently this berg is drifting in an eddy with little change in position during the last 3 days.
